To set up the application environment on Ubunutu 14.04 LTS:

$ sh configure

Use all command line arguments to launch the program:

$ python followers.py --id 1 --nodes 1 --couchip IP_GOES_HERE --consumerkey CONSUMER_KEY --consumersecret CONSUMER_SECRET --tokenkey TOKEN_KEY --tokensecret TOKEN_SECRET

Or as a background process (although it would be better to use a progress manager):

$ nohup python followers.py --id 1 --nodes 1 --couchip IP_GOES_HERE --consumerkey CONSUMER_KEY --consumersecret CONSUMER_SECRET --tokenkey TOKEN_KEY --tokensecret TOKEN_SECRET &
